==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Traversable
<hw>Trav"ers*a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Capable of being traversed, or passed over; <as>as, a
<ex>traversable</ex> region</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Deniable; specifically <fld>(Law)</fld>, liable to
legal objection; <as>as, a <ex>traversable</ex> presentment</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Sir M. Hale.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Traverse</ent>⟦br⟧
